  "content_json": "[{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"text\":\"哈喽大家这里是lala，本期为大家带来SR群体拉条真神幻音千明的攻略！ \"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"text\":\"一图流：\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"text\":\"\"},{\"type\":\"image\",\"key\":\"fNVL8BMGKojO8nzr\",\"src\":\"//cdnimg-v2.gamekee.com/wiki2.0/images/w_3000/h_8482/50364/878729/2025/8/4/945112.png\",\"alt\":\"\",\"isAdaptive\":true,\"style\":{\"width\":\"3000px\",\"height\":\"8482px\"},\"children\":[{\"text\":\"\"}]},{\"text\":\"\"}]},{\"type\":\"header3\",\"children\":[{\"text\":\"一、角色概论 \"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"text\":\"幻音千明是一位集增益、驱散、拉条一体的异格者，由于培养难度低，在前期就有不错的表现，即使是后期，也能在一些副本就业 \"}]},{\"type\":\"header3\",\"children\":[{\"text\":\"二、技能详情 \"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"text\":\"普攻—音涌\",\"bold\":true},{\"text\":\" \"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"text\":\"千明对目标造成伤害，为减益效果最多的队友净化1个减益效果 \"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"text\":\"\"},{\"type\":\"image\",\"key\":\"nhzM5Cq30q93JXzc\",\"src\":\"//cdnimg-v2.gamekee.com/wiki2.0/images/w_3840/h_2160/50364/878729/2025/8/4/526393.png\",\"alt\":\"\",\"isAdaptive\":true,\"style\":{\"width\":\"3840px\",\"height\":\"2160px\"},\"children\":[{\"text\":\"\"}]},{\"text\":\"\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"text\":\"被动—琴心慧\",\"bold\":true}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"text\":\"被动是千明的核心技能，为三名随机队友附加攻击上升，若目标已被附加攻击上升，改为附加提琴颂；需要注意的是，被动在3级之前只会附加攻击上升，5级之前只会为两名队友附加，因此推荐优先点到三级 \"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"text\":\"\",\"bold\":true},{\"type\":\"image\",\"key\":\"15MGmUNgWG71mFbx\",\"src\":\"//cdnimg-v2.gamekee.com/wiki2.0/images/w_3840/h_2160/50364/878729/2025/8/4/565795.png\",\"alt\":\"\",\"isAdaptive\":true,\"style\":{\"width\":\"3840px\",\"height\":\"2160px\"},\"children\":[{\"text\":\"\"}]},{\"bold\":true,\"text\":\"终结技—颂明华\"},{\"text\":\" \"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"text\":\"幻音千明拉条所有队友，并附加攻击上升，若目标已附加攻击上升，再附加提琴颂，由于终结技3级可以直接提升提琴颂的数值，推荐在点满被动后将终结技先升到3级 \"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"text\":\"\"},{\"type\":\"image\",\"key\":\"HzVw7Lh8uS5PtnYT\",\"src\":\"//cdnimg-v2.gamekee.com/wiki2.0/images/w_3840/h_2160/50364/878729/2025/8/4/197256.png\",\"alt\":\"\",\"isAdaptive\":true,\"style\":{\"width\":\"3840px\",\"height\":\"2160px\"},\"children\":[{\"text\":\"\"}]},{\"text\":\"\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"text\":\"推荐加点：被动5级→终结技5级→普攻适当 \",\"bold\":true}]},{\"type\":\"header3\",\"children\":[{\"text\":\"三、矩阵推荐 \"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"text\":\"提琴颂想要做到全覆盖，就需要幻音千明高频率行动，因此推荐1号位和3号位选择速度相关的矩阵，2号位携带有生命加成/防御加成的矩阵，提高生存能力 \"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"text\":\"毕业矩阵：疾驰、生存相关、疾影强袭 \",\"bold\":true}]},{\"type\":\"header3\",\"children\":[{\"text\":\"四、智壳推荐 \"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"text\":\"千明适配许多智壳，万魔法典可以加快提琴颂覆盖，千兆字节保证出手频率，匠提高队伍生存 \"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"text\":\"前期：\",\"bold\":true},{\"text\":\"不羁科学 \"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"text\":\"中期：\",\"bold\":true},{\"text\":\"钻石之心 \"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"text\":\"后期：\",\"bold\":true},{\"text\":\"万魔法典＞千兆字节＞匠 \"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"text\":\"被动推荐：涌流、迅影、影护 \",\"bold\":true}]},{\"type\":\"header3\",\"children\":[{\"text\":\"五、源器推荐 \"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"text\":\"主词条携带生命加成保证生存，副词条优先携带速度保证出手频率 \"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"text\":\"主词条：生命加成*3 \",\"bold\":true}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"text\":\"副词条：速度＞生命加成＞生命 \",\"bold\":true}]},{\"type\":\"header3\",\"children\":[{\"text\":\"六、角色配队 \"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"text\":\"千明技能效果较为泛用，不太局限于特定配队，攻击上升较为适配博尔涅，提高出击频率比较适配罗喉 \"}]}]",
